# Uyghur → IPA transliteration rules (ug_ipa.rules)
#
# Source: McCollum 2021, "Transparency, locality, and contrast in Uyghur backness harmony"
#
# Simplified:
#   - 7-vowel system /ɑ æ e i y ø o u/ (+ marginal /e/)
#   - no explicit [i]~[ɯ] alternation
#   - no diphthongs, no length, no optional allophones in the core map

$V = [ɑ æ e i y ø o u];        # vowel macro (phonemic set used here)

# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------

# One-to-one grapheme → phone map (Uyghur Arabic script)

